{"tid":685290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開車被比中指嗆「滾回中國 」　亞裔歧視又一樁","createTime":"2018-05-31T09:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T10:07:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6aaae22c133cb4a8d8fb0d6e52da7833312e19fb","tid":685290,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"開車被比中指嗆「滾回中國 」　亞裔歧視又一樁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180531/640_e6e8a6b2cddaf29b3a85244cbae71f0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180531%2F640_e6e8a6b2cddaf29b3a85244cbae71f0b.jpg&h=69cea70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n「滾回你的國家，X女人！再見中國！」一家大小開車出遊，卻被另一輛車的車主比中指辱罵，舊金山灣區的亞裔讀者李小姐憤怒不已，拍下這段影片放上臉書。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n李小姐表示，她和老公帶著5歲和10個月大的2個孩子，周一開車到半月灣（Half Moon Bay）旅遊。卻在回程途中遇到一名女駕駛，沒有先切換到右車道，想從馬路中央直接右轉，竟對著綠燈直行的李小姐怒吼，向他們狂飆髒話，叫他們滾回中國，還對著他們豎起中指。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n李小姐非常氣憤，但考慮到兩個小孩都坐在後座，所以老公一直克制脾氣，並盡快把車切到左車道，讓路避開這名種族歧視的女士。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n無獨有偶，上周在舊金山東灣的費利蒙市（Fremont），也有一名韓裔美軍開車時，被白人女駕駛嫌開太慢，開嗆要他「滾出美國」，還對他比拉眼角的羞辱華人動作。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n不過，根據1964年美國《民權法案》，只有因為種族、膚色、宗教等原因，對他人造成或意圖造成身體傷害才算犯罪。所以這兩起歧視案件即使報案，也無法提出刑事告訴。<br />\n（北美中心／綜合外電報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180531/1364360/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180531%2F1364360%2F&d=nmvs43czZi76FBiUJ2hPmS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fcc3ef82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180531%2F1364360%2F&h=27f266c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180531/1364360/</a>"},{"pid":"8397e1444a21a57b23b9caa39b457f2899f8d227","tid":685290,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"亞裔讀者李小姐<br />\n<br />\n支那人就支那人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd79e561d9a816662f89ea6bb21e94f9732c01c","tid":685290,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fd043296233b99c6d0f155af1c7afee0a5a11dc","tid":685290,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20120915/large/1347707310_6182.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20120915%2Flarge%2F1347707310_6182.jpg&h=af2d61a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d0354b0734e437d794f11901533fd1b89e34aff","tid":685290,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}